'''Grime'''（又稱: 车库饶舌）是從西元2000年初在東[[伦敦|倫敦]]出現的一種音樂類型。它由早期的英國[[電子音樂|電子音樂]]風格發展起來，包括[[UK_Garage|UK Garage]]和[[早期叢林舞曲|叢林舞曲]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/grimewave.html|title=Grime Wave|last=McKinnon|first=Matthew|date=2005-05-05|work=[[Canadian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=2007-01-26|archive-date=2007-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070126235949/http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/grimewave.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，同時也受到牙買加[[Dancehall|Dancehall]]、Ragga和[[嘻哈|嘻哈]]的影響<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://uk.complex.com/music/2016/06/hip-hop-dancehall-breaking-down-the-origins-of-grime/dizzee-talks-hip-hop-rosenberg|title=Hip-Hop Or Dancehall? Breaking Down The Grime Scene's Roots|accessdate=|author=|date=2017-02-05|publisher=|archive-date=2017-02-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170206103917/http://uk.complex.com/music/2016/06/hip-hop-dancehall-breaking-down-the-origins-of-grime/dizzee-talks-hip-hop-rosenberg|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這種風格特色是快節奏、切分音碎拍，音樂速度大約在130或140[[速度_(音樂)|bpm]]左右<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/grimewave.html|title=Grime Wave|last=McKinnon|first=Matthew|date=2005-05-05|work=[[Canadian_Broadcasting_Corporation|Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]]|accessdate=2016-01-23|archive-date=2007-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070126235949/http://www.cbc.ca/arts/music/grimewave.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>，時常會伴隨著強烈或鋸齒狀的[[電子音樂|電子音效]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/style/garage-rap-grime-ma0000004464|title=Garage rap/Grime overview|accessdate=9 February 2017|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2017-01-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170119215703/http://www.allmusic.com/style/garage-rap-grime-ma0000004464|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[饒舌|饒舌]]是此風格的重要元素，歌詞常描述阴郁的[[城市|都市生活]]<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nDesCQAAQBAJ&dq=grime+urban+life&source=gbs_navlinks_s|title=UK Hip-Hop, Grime and the City: The Aesthetics and Ethics of London's Rap Scenes|last=Bramwell|first=Richard|publisher=Routledge|year=2012|isbn=|location=|pages=|access-date=2017-02-27|archive-date=2019-06-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612042650/https://books.google.com/books?id=nDesCQAAQBAJ&dq=grime+urban+life&source=gbs_navlinks_s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

這種風格最初透過[[地下電台|地下電台]]（例如[[Rinse_FM|Rinse FM]]）和地下街頭開始傳播。西元2000年中幾位Grime前輩在英國打開知名度，如[[迪利·瑞斯可|迪利·瑞斯可]]、Kano、Lethal Bizzle和Wiley。其他現今知名的歌手有 Ghetts、Jme、Skepta、Stormzy 和 Novelist。知名的Grime團體包括BoyBetterKnow、Newham Generals、Roll Deep和Ruff Sqwad。西元2010年中，Grime音樂類型開始在[[北美地区|北美地區]]受到廣泛關注。

==國內知名度==
Grime音樂從[[2000年代|2000年代]]中期在[[英国|英國]]更受到歡迎，它從[[伦敦|倫敦]]擴散到其他英國大城市。現在來自[[伯明翰|伯明罕]]、[[诺丁汉|諾丁漢]]、[[曼彻斯特|曼徹斯特]]、[[利兹|里茲]]、[[谢菲尔德|謝菲爾德]]和[[布里斯托尔|布里斯托]]的許多Grime歌手透過[[客串|客串]]獲得大量的曝光機會。近期Grime在英國有越來越多在大型活動上演奏的機會，如[[T_in_the_Park|蘇格蘭搖滾音樂節]]、[[Wireless_Festival|無線音樂節]]、[[海德公园|海德公園]]、[[格拉斯顿伯里当代表演艺术节|格拉斯頓伯里當代表演藝術節]]、[[雷丁|雷丁]]及[[利兹|里茲]]。Grime歌手 迪利·瑞斯可於2008年都在這些地點表演過<ref>[http://www.theo2.co.uk/general/lily-allen-and-dizzee-rascal-co-headline-at-the-o2.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.theo2.co.uk/general/lily-allen-and-dizzee-rascal-co-headline-at-the-o2.html |date=20120420045451 }}<nowiki>[1]</nowiki>] O2 reports Dizzee Rascal to play at O2 & Glastonbury</ref><ref>[http://www.nme.com/news/nme/39152 {{Wayback|url=http://www.nme.com/news/nme/39152 |date=20131224125133 }} <nowiki>[2]</nowiki>] NME reports on Dizzee Rascal playing at Reading festival</ref>。

==國際知名度==
===2005-2013===
藉由2005年由[[679_Recordings|679 Recordings唱片公司]]所推出的《Run the Road》全輯時，許多Grime歌手有曝光的機會也提升Grime音樂在國際上的名聲及知名度。

[[女暴君|Lady Sovereign]] 是一位在海外發展成功的Grime歌手，她與[[Jay_Z|Jay-Z]]的音樂製作公司[[Roc-A-Fella_Records|Roc-A-Fella Records]]簽約，曾上過[[大卫·莱特曼晚间秀|大衛深夜秀節目]]。

她的[[单曲|單曲]]《Love Me or Hate Me》登上[[音樂電視網|MTV]]《Total Request Live》第一名也是首位[[英國國籍法|英國籍]][[艺人|艺人]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/story/0,23663,21235541-5007184,00.html |title=Sovereign hits her gold mine |last=Mathewson |first=Catriona |date=2007-02-16 |work=[[The_Courier-Mail|The Courier-Mail]] |publisher=Queensland Newspapers |accessdate=2008-04-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080229051519/http://www.news.com.au/entertainment/story/0%2C23663%2C21235541-5007184%2C00.html |archivedate=2008-02-29 }}</ref>。雖然她早期音樂是透過[[地下電台|地下電台]]的推播，她卻不認為自己是Grime音樂歌手。

迪利·瑞斯可直到2007年發行的第三張專輯《Maths + English》即使沒有在[[美国|美國]]推出卻獲得了國際的贊同。此張專輯受到國際[[音樂評論家|音樂評論家]]、[[杂志|雜誌]]、[[網站|網站]]及[[網誌|部落格]]的高度肯定，包括[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/10309-maths-english/|title=Dizzee Rascal: Maths + English|accessdate=2008-03-12|date=2007-06-15|last=Patrin|first=Nate|work=[[Pitchfork_Media|Pitchfork Media]]|archive-date=2009-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090318181821/http://pitchfork.com/reviews/albums/10309-maths-english/|dead-url=no}}</ref>、[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石雜誌]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/album/14914081/review/14933390/maths__english|title=Maths + English|accessdate=2008-03-12|date=2007-05-30|last=Hoard|first=Christian|work=[[Rolling_Stone|Rolling Stone]] Online|archive-date=2008-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080710133814/http://www.rollingstone.com/reviews/album/14914081/review/14933390/maths__english|dead-url=no}}</ref>和 Rock Sound<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rocksound.tv/articles/166/Dizzee-Rascal---Maths--English.html |title=Dizzee Rascal - Maths & English |accessdate=2008-03-12 |last=Galil |first=Leor |work=[[Rock_Sound|Rock Sound]] |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080616024901/http://www.rocksound.tv/articles/166/Dizzee-Rascal---Maths--English.html |archivedate=2008-06-16 }}</ref>使他再次被提名為一年一度的[[水星音樂獎|水星音樂獎]]。2010年迪利·瑞斯可成功蟬聯三次[[单曲|最佳單曲]]。

===2014-至今===
Grime音樂在[[北美地区|北美地區]]越來越受到歡迎。Skepta與北美地區合作過的[[歌手|歌手藝人]]有[[德雷克_(歌手)|德雷克]]、[[Ace_Hood|Ace Hood]]、[[Earl_Sweatshirt|Earl Sweatshirt]]、[[ASAP_Mob|ASAP Mob]]和[[Flatbush_Zombie|Flatbush Zombie]]，使他成為在[[美国|美國]]和[[加拿大|加拿大]]最知名的Grime歌手<ref>Dexter, Thomas. "POP & HISS; Noble Grime; Paintings Grandly Honor Heroes of a Pop Genre." Los Angeles TimesOct 27 2015. ProQuest. Web. 15 Feb. 2016 .</ref>。這股風潮也傳到[[澳大利亚|澳大利亞]]、[[日本|日本]]和[[荷兰|荷蘭]]。日本受到的風格影響最深，近期出現許多「日式Grime」日本與[[英国|英國]]的Grime歌手互相合作<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://ukf.com/words/mc-duff-and-the-rise-of-japanese-grime/18472|title=MC Duff and the rise of Japanese grime|accessdate=2017-01-27|date=2017-01-27|publisher=UKF.com|language=EN|archive-date=2018-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180404201101/https://ukf.com/words/mc-duff-and-the-rise-of-japanese-grime/18472|dead-url=no}}</ref>。歌手Skepta於2016年推出專輯Konnichiwa，也在同年五月於[[东京|東京]]的酒吧Boiler Room演出。[[2017年全英音樂獎|2017年全英音樂獎]]上[[紅髮艾德|紅髮愛德]]首次與Grime歌手Stormzy合演出《Shape of You》<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.xxlmag.com/video/2017/02/stormzy-performs-shape-of-you-ed-sheeran-2017-brit-awards/|title=Stormzy Performs “Shape of You” With Ed Sheeran at 2017 Brit Awards|accessdate=2017-03-04|author=Justin Ivey|date=2017-02-22|publisher=XXL|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629134729/https://www.xxlmag.com/video/2017/02/stormzy-performs-shape-of-you-ed-sheeran-2017-brit-awards/|dead-url=no}}</ref>兩天後(24日)此[[单曲|單曲]][[ITunes|線上發行]]。

==爭議==
Grime音樂同樣也遭受到世界上許多類似的反對聲浪，特別是來自政府的官員[[Kim_Howells|Kim Howells]]曾做出評論說：宣稱發現Grime音樂支持者有「強烈種族主義」<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2003/jan/06/ukguns.immigrationpolicy1|title=Minister labelled racist after attack on rap 'idiots'|last=Gibbons|first=Fiachra|date=2003-01-06|work=[[The_Guardian|The Guardian]]|publisher=[[Guardian_Media_Group|Guardian Media Group]]|accessdate=2008-03-13|archive-date=2013-08-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130826204410/http://www.theguardian.com/uk/2003/jan/06/ukguns.immigrationpolicy1|dead-url=no}}</ref>但美國音樂評論家[[Jeff_Chang|Jeff Chang]]在[[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]]文章中提出了反駁的觀點，他說[[Dizzee_Rascal|Dizzee Rascal]]的歌詞中經常提及暴力及性方面的字眼是在「捕捉、封裝、保存」每天與同伴在街上所見的生活<ref name="future">{{cite web|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/music/0403,chang,50366,22.html|title=Future Shock|accessdate=2008-03-12|date=2004-01-13|last=Chang|first=Jeff|authorlink=Jeff Chang (journalist)|work=[[The_Village_Voice|The Village Voice]]|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080328234033/http://www.villagevoice.com/music/0403%2Cchang%2C50366%2C22.html|archivedate=2008-03-28}}</ref>。

